FBIS4-13419 "drnes076_s_94004" FBIS-NES-94-076 Daily Report 19 Apr 1994 Iran President, Greek Prime Minister Discuss Gorazde on Phone President, Greek Prime Minister Discuss Gorazde on Phone LD1904172694 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network in Persian 1630 GMT 19 Apr 94 LD1904172694 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network Persian BFN [Excerpt] Mr. Hashemi-Rafsanjani has held a telephone conversation with the Greek prime minister and current chairman of the European Union. In this conversation, President Hashemi-Rafsanjani said: Islamic countries expect that the EU should either take action to stop the Serbian genocide of Muslims, or allow other countries to help the Bosnian people. [passage omitted]
